  Rob Arnott , chairman of Research 
Affiliates LLC, favors emerging-market stocks.  The price of 
options to protect against emerging market equity losses has 
climbed to its highest since 2009 relative to U.S. contracts.  
Bloomberg Radio's Catherine Cowdery reports on Exchange Traded 
Funds.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 01:31
 